text: Rina Dewi Puspitasari is an archer from Indonesia. She was born on 5 October 1985. Dewi Puspitasari competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics.Rina Dewi PuspitasariRina Dewi PUSPITASARI == References == Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian archers Category:Olympians for Indonesia
